<div style="margin-bottom:20px;">
  <div style="font-size:15px; font-weight:800; color:#92400e; margin-bottom:6px;">Demann <%= @amount_display %> Ekspire</div>
  <div style="font-size:13px; color:#5D6345;">Demann #<%= @payment_request.id %> — <%= @payment_request.updated_at.strftime("%b %d, %Y") %></div>
</div>

<div style="background:#fef3c7; border:2px solid #92400e; border-radius:14px; padding:16px; margin-bottom:16px;">
  <table width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
    <tr>
      <td style="color:#92400e; font-size:12px; font-weight:600; padding-bottom:8px;">Montan Mande</td>
      <td style="color:#2E2E38; font-weight:800; text-align:right; padding-bottom:8px;"><%= @amount_display %></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="color:#92400e; font-size:12px; font-weight:600; padding-bottom:8px;">Lajan</td>
      <td style="color:#2E2E38; font-weight:700; text-align:right; padding-bottom:8px;"><%= @payment_request.asset_label %></td>
    </tr>
    <% if @payment_request.payer_name.present? %>
      <tr>
        <td style="color:#92400e; font-size:12px; font-weight:600;">Peyè</td>
        <td style="color:#2E2E38; font-weight:600; text-align:right;"><%= @payment_request.payer_name %></td>
      </tr>
    <% end %>
    <tr>
      <td colspan="2" style="border-top:1px dashed #92400e; padding-top:10px;"></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="color:#92400e; font-size:13px; font-weight:900; text-transform:uppercase;">Estati</td>
      <td style="color:#92400e; font-size:18px; font-weight:900; text-align:right;">EKSPIRE</td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</div>

<% if @payment_request.expires_at.present? %>
  <div style="background:#fff; border:1px solid #d9d6c4; border-radius:12px; padding:12px; margin-bottom:16px;">
    <div style="color:#5D6345; font-size:10px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1px; margin-bottom:4px;">Dat Ekspirasyon</div>
    <div style="color:#2E2E38; font-size:13px;"><%= @payment_request.expires_at.strftime("%b %d, %Y %l:%M %p").strip %></div>
  </div>
<% end %>

<div style="font-size:13px; color:#5D6345; line-height:1.6;">
  Demann peman ou ekspire paske li pa t resevwa peman anvan dat limit la. Ou ka kreye yon nouvo demann si ou bezwen.
</div>
